## Common Test Utilities

```python
def create_test_brain_data(n_images=10, n_voxels=100):
    """Helper to create test data."""
    data = np.random.randn(n_images, n_voxels)
    return Brain_Data(data=data)

def assert_brain_data_equal(brain1, brain2):
    """Custom assertion for Brain_Data equality."""
    assert_array_almost_equal(brain1.data, brain2.data)
    assert brain1.shape() == brain2.shape()
    if brain1.Y is not None:
        assert_array_almost_equal(brain1.Y, brain2.Y)
```